<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Christy Shake</span></strong> lives in Brunswick, Maine, with her ten-year-old son, Calvin, and her photographer husband, Michael Kolster. She writes a blog about her son and his epilepsy at <a href="http://calvinsstory.com">calvinsstory.com</a>, and she is working on a memoir. Her essay in this issue is her first published work.</p><a href="/contributors/christy-shake" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
